A Dark Night 's Passing ( 暗夜行路 An'ya Kōro ) is the only full - length novel by Japanese writer Shiga Naoya . It was written in serialized form and published in Kaizo in between 1921 and 1937 . It candidly follows the experiences of a young Japanese bachelor . English translation : Shiga Naoya , Trans . Edwin McClellan ( 1993 - reissue ) . A Dark Night 's Passing . May 1990 , paperback ( Eng . Image : Books - aj.svg aj ashton 01b.svgThis article on a 1920s novel is a stub . 